{"lemma":"دَعَةٌ","slug":"دَعَةٌ","root":"#.د.ع","root_slug":"_-د-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/_-د-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n44501"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"calmness, comfort, prosperity, welfare"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/da.ʕa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n44501","headword_ar":"دَعَةٌ","root":"wdE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ease; repose; freedom from trouble or inconvenience, and toil or fatigue; tranquillity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xafoDN","text_ar":"خَفْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S. Mgh, K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAHapN","text_ar":"رَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sukuwnN","text_ar":"سُكُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ampleness of circumstances"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEapN","text_ar":"سَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":") in life: (K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEapN","text_ar":"دَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rAHp","text_ar":"راحة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"skwn","text_ar":"سكون"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xafoDN","text_ar":"خَفْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies “ ampleness of the circumstances ” ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEah~N","text_ar":"سَعَهٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":") of life, and “ plentifulness and pleasantness ” thereof: [see an ex. of both, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xafoDN","text_ar":"خَفْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (El-Marzookee